Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼辦好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.15,0:00:08.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在考慮嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.95,0:00:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三週年特別企劃的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.44,0:00:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只剩下2天了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.25,0:00:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是有新創作的長篇朗讀劇嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還需要什麼別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.41,0:00:19.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.77,0:00:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白的店長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.49,0:00:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有朗讀劇的話 和平常做的沒什麼不同
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.28,0:00:25.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.64,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得的3週年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.44,0:00:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想做些有驚喜的特別的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  那麼我們乾脆來拍個電影咋樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提議 要是拍電影的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想拍獵奇類的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.55,0:00:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努蟲被殭屍襲擊 努蟲爆炸這種的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,+++嘔吐注意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.51,0:00:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就沒人權了嗎喂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.85,0:00:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也挺喜歡獵奇類的誒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒？殭屍來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.71,0:00:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,電影…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.15,0:00:54.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就不用說了 你想拍哪種類型
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.98,0:00:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很明…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.83,0:00:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\p1\an5\fscx30\fscy325\shad0\bord1\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H50&\3c&H000000&\pos(211,1010)}m 0 0 l -200 -200 l 200 -200 l 200 20 l -200 20 l -200 -200
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.08,0:00:57.83,shufa@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(91,361)}阿佐谷救世主传说
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.36,0:00:59.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想演被救世主從地面上拔起的那把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這也太卑屈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.50,0:01:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爭取下人權啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 溢 溢出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.62,0:01:12.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛…眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.27,0:01:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會因為你 消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.75,0:01:22.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前也有聽到過…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.69,0:01:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.12,0:01:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.71,0:01:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會導致陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.70,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(656,459)}知曉吧 出生的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.72,0:03:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Deava是對NESTA 對文字怪獸的特殊機關
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.40,0:03:19.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果陽的異變是因為文字的影響
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:20.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那這裡應該會有什麼數據才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.99,0:03:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擅自進行連接很危險的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警備系統會啟動的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.51,0:03:33.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該不是在玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:38.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 請借給我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:41.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敬您是個頂天立地的漢子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,表面上是個普通的圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.20,0:03:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是在其的地下…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.96,0:03:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是聚集了古代文字文明相關資料的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.05,0:03:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府管理下的保管設施
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:05.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這些也只是被隱藏起來的資料的一小部分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為大部分都交給了NESTA
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.96,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要趕快查哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是被發現了 要負責的可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是你失業了 「白箱」負起責任僱傭你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.53,0:04:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健人原本不就是「白箱」的店員嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.44,0:04:25.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是政府的派遣人員
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.23,0:04:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同時還負責管理著這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.01,0:04:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果陽君的身體發生了某些異變
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:37.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那其原因是餓號機的可能性非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.98,0:04:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是因為那架Vector嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我們的責任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.12,0:04:44.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明明知道那架機體非常的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.16,0:04:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他是為了拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑自己的意志登上那架機體的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.31,0:04:53.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們現在應該去做的事就不是去後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡最大的努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.87,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不能讓他犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是描寫文字戰爭場景的抽像畫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文字戰爭？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:09.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說在過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:13.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人名擁有將聲音所描述之物具現化的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.30,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說 這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.31,0:05:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為說出了「雨」這個字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.97,0:05:20.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會實際真的下起雨來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種事真的能做到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.04,0:05:25.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,適當的時間 適當的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.49,0:05:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們通過發出包含著意念的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.65,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功連接到了真理的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.53,0:05:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了眼前的每一刻都竭盡全力的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻無法給後世留下些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要留下自己的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.07,0:05:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去傳達
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.43,0:05:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了實現他們的這個欲求
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們創造了某樣東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是文字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為能夠傳達給遠方的他人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且能給後世遺留的文字的出現
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,文明開始了飛速的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.80,0:06:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 也有一些種族因此而產生了危機感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們警告世人 過於依賴文字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.82,0:06:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就會慢慢失去連通真理世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想繼續發展文字和文明的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和想繼續探索真理世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最終產生了衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而後發起的爭戰 就是文字戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.66,0:06:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:29.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人也從來沒對我說過這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.07,0:06:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他覺得這些你並不需要知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.72,0:06:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要想讓人盲目相信某種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最好的辦法就是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.84,0:06:37.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有選擇的給予對方信息 縮小其視野
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個女生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.99,0:06:43.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是什麼象徵人物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,具體的就不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 關於聽命於她的這個巨人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.00,0:06:52.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有資料記錄表明其名字是「殺戮天使」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭最終是以文字種族的勝利 落下了帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.45,0:07:01.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然其過程有很多不清楚的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過有一點是可以確定的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.12,0:07:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終結這場戰爭的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.44,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.59,0:07:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,aquarion Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,aquarion Logos...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.20,0:07:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Aquarion Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.59,0:07:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對這個名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果毫無收穫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,司令 關於陽...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.21,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時還是向創聲部的大家保密吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不要告訴陽本人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本人不告訴他真的沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不應該告訴他餓號機的危險性
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時禁止他出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.81,0:07:50.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論說什麼 那傢伙都會去戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他就是這樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:58.21,post,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fnFZYouXian-Z09\an8}限定菜單案企劃會議
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.88,0:07:58.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目標是女性客戶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.77,0:08:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為女性最喜歡「限定」這種詞了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯 很容易就會被吸引住而排隊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此我想 限定菜單就多添加一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,容易被女性接受的健康菜單
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.69,0:08:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,健康菜單是指沙拉什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.72,0:08:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種東西根本吃不飽啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.09,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多添加些有份量的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸雞塊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.34,0:08:20.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,油炸食品可是健康大敵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再說做起來也太麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:23.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雞…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我來養吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會從養殖開始啊喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.53,0:08:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想吃漢堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.52,0:08:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漢堡肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.90,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要牛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.92,0:08:40.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要自己養的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.73,0:08:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要不就做健康的漢堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.14,0:08:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,贊成 櫻子也最愛漢堡肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.40,0:08:48.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那從現在開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.76,0:08:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員開始創造健康的原創漢堡肉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 我們也要做嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全員參加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.52,0:09:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男生組漢堡肉 完成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:05.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人做的是豆腐漢堡肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.47,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,標準的素食漢堡肉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努蟲做的這個形狀...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.14,0:09:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼啊 是漢堡肉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.29,0:09:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:16.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用豆腐做漢堡肉也太普通了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我用漢堡肉做了豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.29,0:09:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個方形肉塊吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.10,0:09:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君的倒是很普通呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 雖然外表看起來還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.98,0:09:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過最重要的還是味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.15,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺嘴裡有什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\p1\an5\fscx30\fscy200\shad0\bord1\c&HFAF8F1&\1a&H50&\3c&H000000&\pos(248,788)}m 0 0 l -200 -200 l 200 -200 l 200 20 l -200 20 l -200 -200
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:40.40,shufa@,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(136,377)}低卡洛里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:40.69,*Default,,0,0,0,,放了這個進去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請至少做出可以吃的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:46.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來可以成為戰力的只有翼人做的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.59,0:09:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那接下來就輪到女生了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.97,0:09:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 小心音和舞亞也快點來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.43,0:09:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會做料理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做給他吃的話 陽君肯定會很開心的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:01.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來來 自己也試試
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:03.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}別亂來 我自己會吃的 要問為什麼的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.80,0:10:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞 用力過度了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.33,0:10:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好難啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.00,0:10:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要這樣 這樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.50,0:10:14.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.38,0:10:16.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.21,0:10:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像捏死文字怪獸那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.09,0:10:19.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小花嵐 不可以告訴她錯誤的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:24.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我最後一擊 文字怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.18,0:10:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.63,0:10:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也不要真聽她的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.32,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:39.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你到底是從哪兒學來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 好好吃的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.78,0:10:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誒 為什麼倒掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,味 味道沒有調好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這 這 這樣的 沒法吃啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我要拯救我的胃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.24,0:11:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}這才對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說難吃不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.26,0:11:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞果然變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是恢復成正常人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.52,0:11:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恢復成和年齡相符的女孩子的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:57.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,材料浪費太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.76,0:11:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵 吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.22,0:12:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我不是自告奮勇出來買了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麻煩的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.92,0:12:07.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你自己要跟來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:12.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是不好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.52,0:12:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要坐一會兒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.95,0:12:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就去買個東西 這是不是有點太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:20.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該不是跑哪裡去說甜言蜜語了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:24.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你嫉妒了嗎 明明有我這麼可愛的女朋友在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.24,0:12:26.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.62,0:12:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和試吃不同的 我特別準備的便當哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.64,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翔子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迴避
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.99,0:12:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.53,0:12:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.43,0:12:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是發生了什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.98,0:12:44.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是身體不是很舒服而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼情況
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有事想要問你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於劍崎總的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很在意嗎 我和總是怎樣的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.13,0:13:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定不能落下風了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.62,0:13:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再次碰上的話 一定要打倒他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.04,0:13:07.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想要更瞭解一點 關於他的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.91,0:13:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總他的精神有些不穩定
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明實力應該很不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.44,0:13:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻總是因為自己的不成熟而拖後腿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法發揮出真正的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.80,0:13:26.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又有些過於自信 破綻繁多
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,動不動就會放鬆警惕 缺乏判斷力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一個優點都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.82,0:13:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 他也不是個壞人 優點還是有的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.53,0:13:39.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他以前…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:40.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.16,0:13:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候 正好也是像現在這樣明月當空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時我非常苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.86,0:13:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至痛苦到希望自己能消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就一直那樣哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:14:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總究竟說了什麼 我現在已經記不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.46,0:14:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 因為他的話我獲得了救贖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.80,0:14:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,覺得自己又能努力活下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:10.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了啊 你在生什麼氣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.39,0:14:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒什麼 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:38.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.42,0:14:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.80,0:14:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…不想失去…陽…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.97,0:14:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不會讓你消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.47,0:15:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NESTA應該保留有很多文字文明的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.21,0:15:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會有的 拯救陽的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:24.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該早就被察覺到了才對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻沒有見到警備員行動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.88,0:15:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來得真晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.73,0:15:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定已經想到了吧 我會在這裡這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.76,0:15:43.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但即使是這樣 我也不會妨礙到你找資料
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要把我抓住當人質 就能成為助你逃出這裡的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.27,0:15:50.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還真是被小看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:51.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.18,0:15:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼會知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是當然的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為你就是我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.31,0:16:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你能看得到我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.24,0:16:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然這是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:10.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像這樣見面還是第一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.80,0:16:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祝 開業三週年
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:18.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒到時間啊 不可以偷跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有小心音在就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,翼人君 來一份帥哥成份兩倍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等全員都到了再說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:29.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼還沒有到呢 舞亞和陽君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.77,0:16:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞也不在「電子白箱又快那裡 到底去哪裡了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.07,0:16:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽…君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然會為了保護灰吹陽 而一個人到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.23,0:16:58.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是一心一意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.16,0:17:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道些什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.53,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要消滅灰吹陽的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你們稱為餓號機的那個機體的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.97,0:17:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種不祥的力量會吞噬他的概念 最終讓其消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:16.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再這樣下去 灰吹陽這個概念就會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道這意味著什麼嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了概念的他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.93,0:17:25.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會變成誰都看不到 認知不到的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.17,0:17:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不僅如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總有一天 他的概念也會消失在人們的記憶中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起度過的時間 共同創造的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也都會從大家的腦中消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.30,0:17:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你心中的灰吹陽 也終有一天會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.55,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會 陽他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.59,0:17:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悲傷嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你沒有資格擁有這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.31,0:17:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是說過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會消失都是因為你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.01,0:17:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灰吹陽他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.67,0:17:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是成為了替身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.53,0:18:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.94,0:18:04.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我裡面好好呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.28,0:18:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餓號機真正想抹消掉的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.58,0:18:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餓號機是過去的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.30,0:18:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了打倒Aquarion Logos 而創造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它的存在意義
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.64,0:18:25.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在已經過去1萬2前年的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.73,0:18:27.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也仍然傳承了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:29.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在文字戰爭中出現的aquarion Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:36.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是由兩個人駕駛的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.67,0:18:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一人就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.63,0:18:41.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NESTA
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NESTA…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.87,0:18:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後另一個駕駛者
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.24,0:18:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是我的摯愛之人桐生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,aquarion Logos
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在戰爭中被打敗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和桐生都死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.34,0:18:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.24,0:18:59.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在現代出現了想要得到我們力量之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.34,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是父親
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莊嚴大人他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.85,0:19:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父親他渴望著aquarion Logos的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.87,0:19:12.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他跨越1萬2千年的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在眾星的指引下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尋找到了那個注定成為桐生的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 他…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.69,0:19:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍崎總就是過去的aquarion Logos操縱者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.32,0:19:28.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,繼承桐生意志之人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.96,0:19:31.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和總一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你出身的意義
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.08,0:19:39.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從融入Logos世界的我的靈魂中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創造出了另一個關鍵的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:44.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憑借總的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.16,0:19:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.53,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.02,0:19:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來了 成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.94,0:19:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以創聲力為觸媒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用NESTA的靈魂種創造才出的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是創聲人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.13,0:20:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你 舞亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:08.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙 騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.72,0:20:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我的代替品而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.52,0:20:20.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人偶小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:23.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和人偶一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.33,0:20:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,騙人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:35.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我得到創聲之書的力量之前我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.42,0:20:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 說忘掉了更合適吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於你出生時的記憶都被封印了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是現在我什麼都想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.17,0:20:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,包括在父親面前從Logos世界中創造出你的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.63,0:20:52.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出生時的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父母的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.72,0:20:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有想過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從沒有過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.29,0:21:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為創造時就設定成讓你不會去想那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.63,0:21:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.39,0:21:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓天空…哭泣了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.72,0:21:18.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是真理的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.71,0:21:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為和總在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.69,0:21:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以發揮出了平常無法發揮的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然只在限定情況下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.60,0:21:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這力量和我的力量的本質相同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.17,0:21:31.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 這下你就明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於你自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:43.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可憐的人偶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少讓我幫你在沒有任何痛苦下結束一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.72,0:21:50.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面雨下的好大的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼這樣 難得的紀念日
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陽君…你來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.62,0:22:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞亞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.22,0:22:12.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 結束一切吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.18,0:22:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是這場戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.44,0:22:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.57,0:23:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小翔子 快看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沖繩特產 最高級的金楚糕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.59,0:23:56.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努蟲興奮過頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想看女朋友的笑容而已
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.48,0:23:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鬼一邊涼快去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說誰是小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 努蟲你嘴邊有殘渣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.35,0:24:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下集 第二十一話 悲壯 背德的合體
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.32,0:24:09.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戀愛真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.01,0:00:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
